      "acceptanceCriteria": "Verification that the ML surrogate implementation reproduces analytical or reference solutions for limiting cases.",
      "rationale": "Limiting-case checks confirm that the surrogate returns zero hemolysis index for zero shear-stress input and reproduces the power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger reference values at three benchmark shear levels. Required level 1 is met."
