      "rationale": "All validation experiments and CFD simulations used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under flow and speed conditions representative of clinical CPB use. The validation domain matches the intended COU. However, validation was conducted exclusively at nominal operating conditions; no assessment of surrogate behaviour under geometry perturbations, manufacturing tolerance variations, or shifted patient-population haematocrit was included. Real-world distribution shift is stated as studied separately with no linked evidence."
    },
    {
